ports_menu () {

common_message "ðŸš€  Ports - Menu Interface" "
ðŸ’¬  Further Explanation? Visit ~ https://plexguide.com/wiki/ports/
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[D] By Default Ports: [$default_port]
[2] Client ID           : [$ci_menu]
